data.description: This is a quaint 3 bedroom 1 bath,  1,148 sqft home just a few minutes North of The Dallas Lovefield Airport. This property offers multiple exit strategies for all investors. The area is currently being revitalized as properties are being demolished and mansions are being rebuilt. This property offers opportunity for eager investors whom would like to renovate the property and resell it quickly and lastly it offers flexibility for long term investors whom enjoy airbnb hosting due to its central and convenient location. The property has brick exterior, original hardwood floors, and a partially updated kitchen. The kitchen has new white shaker cabinets and new porcelain floors. The remainder of the home has original qualities. This is an as-is sale, no repairs or concessions will be given as this is priced well below land value. WILL NOT QUALIFY FOR CONVENTIONAL FINANCING CASH OR HARD MONEY ONLY.
